+## Evaluator Contract
+
+評価結果は STDOUT に JSON 1 オブジェクトで返す:
+
+```json
+{
+  "rubric_id": "{{rubric_id}}",
+  "rubric_version": "{{rubric_version}}",
+  "rubric_hash": "<sha256:rubric.json>",
+  "target": "<path>",
+  "score": 0,
+  "threshold": {{threshold | default(80)}},
+  "passed": false,
+  "findings": [{"id":"...","severity":"high|medium|low","message":"..."}],
+  "required_fixes": [],
+  "pending_human": []
+}
+```
+
+**禁則**: 被採点物の Write/Edit を持たない。rubric も改変しない。評価ログは `eval-log/skill-build-trace.jsonl` へ append（F1 規約）。
+
